# Martinrea AP frontend — Supabase configuration.
# Copy to .env and fill in from your Supabase project: Settings → API.
#   VITE_SUPABASE_URL       = Project URL (https://<ref>.supabase.co)
#   VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY  = Project API key (anon / publishable — safe in the client)
